data.description: Welcome home to 1727 Diving Duck Lane.  This beautiful open floor plan offers plenty of opportunity for entertaining!  Hardwood floors throughout the whole first floor.  When you first walk in, your immediately welcomed by a flex space (currently being used as a tv/game area) and a formal dining area.  Keep walking to the living room and kitchen area, which also has a large eat in area.  Lots of cabinet space!  Also downstairs is the large laundry room and half bathroom.  Upstairs you'll walk right into a large loft area.  HUGE master bedroom with ensuite is also upstairs.  Separate tub/shower as well as His and Hers separate closets!  3 additional secondary bedrooms and a guest bath are also upstairs.  This home has a nice size screened in porch and fenced in backyard!  Come check it out
